    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25409302_4_5997-6166",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "5997-6166",
      "markText": "偶然相遇便依依不舍， 一来二去已堕入情网； 刚尝到甜头又生出怨恨， 幸福之中就有哀痛滋长， 如此这般凑成小说一部。",
      "totalCount": 630,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25409302&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=5997&rangeEnd=6166",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/61c32f307183b71661c671f?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=5997&rangeEnd=6166"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25409302_7_546-740",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "546-740",
      "markText": "如今，唉！哲学、 法学和医学， 遗憾还有神学， 我全已努力钻研。 可到头来仍是个傻瓜， 并未比当初聪明半点！",
      "totalCount": 612,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=25409302&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=546&rangeEnd=740",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/61c32f307183b71661c671f?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=546&rangeEnd=740"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "25409302_5_5089-5220",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "5089-5220",
      "markText": "人在努力时太容易松懈， 很快会爱上绝对的清闲； 因此我乐意造一个魔鬼， 让他刺激人，与人作伴。",
